com.project.searching

Class GasStation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.project.searching.GasStation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class GasStation
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Stores the data associated with a gas station. Implements the Parcelable interface, allowing it to be added to the Bundle of extended data passed between activities.

    • Constructor Detail

      • GasStation

        GasStation(java.lang.String stationId,
          java.lang.String stationName,
          com.google.android.gms.maps.model.LatLng coords,
          StationAddress address,
          FuelPrice selectedPrice,
          double distance)
        Constructs a new GasStation with a myGasFeed id, name, coordinates, street address, FuelPrice, and distance from start location. Used when the data was obtained for a user search request
        Parameters:
        stationId - the myGasFeed ID for the station
        stationName - the name of the station
        coords - the (latitude, longitude) coordinate of the station
        address - the street address of the station
        selectedPrice - the FuelPrice (based on the user's selected fuel type)
        distance - the distance of the station from the start point used to make the myGasFeed request

      • GasStation

        GasStation(java.lang.String stationId,
          java.lang.String stationName,
          com.google.android.gms.maps.model.LatLng coords,
          StationAddress address,
          FuelPrice reg,
          FuelPrice mid,
          FuelPrice pre,
          FuelPrice diesel)
        Constructs a new GasStation with a myGasFeed id, name, coordinates, street address, and the FuelPrice for all of the fuel types (reg, mid, pre and diesel). Used when the data was obtained by retrieving a station by its myGasFeed id.
        Parameters:
        stationId - the myGasFeed ID for the station
        stationName - the name of the station
        coords - the (latitude, longitude) coordinate of the station
        address - the street address of the station
        reg - the FuelPrice for regular fuel
        mid - the FuelPrice for mid fuel
        pre - the FuelPrice for premium fuel
        diesel - the FuelPrice for diesel fuel
